Ever wonder if those YouTube sponsors are actually worth it? I spent hundreds of dollars testing Fum, Raycon, AG1, DeleteMe, Verb energy bars and G2A to find out which ones are legitimate and which ones are... questionable. From $170 headphones that sound terrible to energy bars with sketchy subscription tactics, the results might surprise you.
